Spain May Raise Gas, Tobacco, Alcohol Taxes, Economista Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-08-26T06:36:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-26/spain-may-raise-gas-tobacco-alcohol-taxes-economista-says.html
Spain  may consider raising taxes
applied to tobacco, alcohol and gas consumption,  El Economista 
reported, citing people familiar with the matter.  The government may consider the plan as funding costs for
the country increase, the Madrid-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
